</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-jHkVzv iFnjrD pf-24_ pf-text-1"><strong>Scope</strong> - The RQIA regulates various services, including hospitals, nursing homes, domiciliary care agencies, and residential care homes.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-jHkVzv iFnjrD pf-26_ pf-text-1"><strong>Inspections</strong> - In 2022 alone, the RQIA conducted over 500 inspections across various health and social care settings.

































































